commit.title: Match goals in diffs correctly based on comparing the underlying proofs.
commit.message:
Match goals in diffs correctly based on comparing the underlying proofs.
This means that if goal 1 had diffs, then "all: swap 1 2" will show those
diffs in goal 2 of the context.  Also "2: split" will correctly show the
diff on goal 2.
